content.text: Welcome to the Halloween!
Did you come here to become|a Dynamon Captain?
Let's start by testing your SKILLS!
NICE! you have great potential.|Now choose your own Dynamon!
Great choice, you will make a great team!
Now, I have something to give you...
These ITEMS will be useful in your journey.
Speaking of which,|let's find a WILD DYNAMON...
Let's find some wild|Dynamons to BATTLE!
WAIT! Now that it's weak, let's|try to CATCH it!
WOW! Your Dynamon can LEVEL UP!
We use SHARDS to do that.|Use some now!
You can SWITCH Dynamons during battle.
Let's use the Duxedo you just caught!
That's Sofia, she is a trainer like you...
Go and BATTLE her!
During battles, you can use one ITEM per turn.
Use the SKILL CAN you just got!
Dynamons and Skills have TYPES...
Use the STRONG type when possible!
WOW, you're STRONG!|But I'm stronger!
Next time i won't lose!
You got access to a new location.
Let's go there!
Hi! My name is Julian...
Let's practice our battle technique!
Maybe I'm too old for this...
Great adventure ahead, | stay safe, my dear.
Meet me at the haunted castle,|if you dare!
But you will be scared soon Blaze.
Even the Elite will not make it till| the end of this road.
Thanks Julian for calling in the Elite!
Challenge me at the haunted mansion|and win the ultimate Halloween fire Dynamon!
A legendary fire Dynamon!| Now that sounds like a challenge for me!
I'm the Earth Elite! There is nothing that would scare me!
That is a lot of big talk.|You did not reach the end of the road yet.
I am on my way!|Mister Pumpkin is going to see me first!
The Water Elite is here to win the challenge!
Proof it and win this battle first!
We need to call in the boss!|This Mister Pumpkin is up to some plan.
Why was my Elite team send here?|Who gave those orders?
I am the boss here!
Meet me if you dare Klaude!
We need stop wasting time from the Elite!
We have guards to do the dirty work! Guards| get to the end of that haunted castle! NOW!
Yes sur! We are on our way!
The boss has ordered us to reach the end of this road first!
We will stop anyone who gets in our way!
Ouch! I got bitten by some crazy bat!
I am starting to feel weird and I am so hungry!
I think I want to eat...
I want to eat brains!
Hungry! Give me your brain!
Get out my way you weird Zombie!
haha I think the Zombie missed me!
Why are you sweating and itching|on your head all the time?
The Fire Elite is now under my control Mwahahaha
Fire Elite I order you to give our guests | a special halloween challenge!
Yes master! As you wish!
I dare you to win 5 matches in the captain battles!
Well done!
Looks like Blaze is out! | This place was too scary for him!
I'm not a coward! You think some | pumpkin man is going to scare me!
Hungry! Let me have you for lunch!
I'm not your lunch. Go away!
Just 1 small bite from your tasty arm!!
The only thing that scares me is a werewolf.
I am not scared of any zombie!
Owoooooooooooooh!
That's it! Forgot about it! I'm outta it here!
Mwhahahah. All it took was the Devish | evolution Wereboar to scare Julian.
You don't smell tasty! I need something | more crunchy instead!
It seems the boy got lucky and managed | to escape the Zombie without getting bitten.
Why is this Zombie looking at me?
Yes! Brains with some crunchy rocks!
Where is this Zombie now? | Did the Zombie bite me????
I see him chewing over there on something! | He has a piece from your rock armor.
Delicious crunchy rock armor!
The zombie only took a bite out of my armor right?
Why is the earth elite starting to look green?
Soon the Earth Elite will join my army of Monsters.
Get lost Pumpkin head! | I will never take any order from you!
The transformation from the Earth Elite is complete! | The Frankenstein monster is alive!
I feel so strong master! | Let me challenge the boy!
I will bet you can't even win 5 matches in the captain battles!
I can't believe I lost this bet.
No Zombie took a bite out of me yet!
Why am I so thirsty?
I feel so strange... and I am...
so thirsty... for blood!
Out of my way Zombie fools! I will punch | you out of my way with my fists!
I punched 1 of those Zombies out of | here with an uppercut punch move!
Chuk, did you just say you touched that Zombie?
You worry too much! I took care of that Zombie.
These other zombies don't taste good. | We need fresh meat!
Yes! This guy has more meat | on his arm to chew on for us.
You want some of this! | Come and get it and feel the power of my fist!
I scared away those Zombies! | They got scared of my powerful fist!
Give me that arm!
Where did that Zombie come from? | He just came out of nowhere and scratched me!
You can't escape destiny Chuk. | You will join our Zombie Army soon!
Give in to that hunger Chuk!
No . . .  I . . .  can . . .|  fight . . .  this . . .
I feel so . . . hungry! I want to eat the . . .
Why is the Zombie looking at me?
I want to eat the Water Elite!
No way! I want to stay pretty. | You are not changing me into a green slimy monster!
I have a plan! I'm going to fool those stupid zombies!
Can you keep the Zombies busy?| Meanwhile I will dress up into a pirate.
I will pretend I got bitten by a Zombie and | say he turned me into a zombie pirate.
I was able to change into this Pirate clothing!
Now we need to fool these Zombies and | tell them that I got changed into a zombie pirate.
(Play along with me here). | Ahoy! Give me your brain!
Huh? Who is that?
Arrrr. I am so hungry! | (I guess I should say that right?)
This pirate zombie smells weird.
She smells fresh!
That pirate makes me hungry.
Yes she is fresh meat!
Noooooo! That stupid zombie just scratched me!
That pirate will join us soon!
Nooooo I don't want to look green and ugly!
I am starting . . . to . . . feel . . .
I feel hungry and . . . powerful!
And another one has joined our Zombie Army. | Mwahahahaha!
What?!!! That Pumpkin idiot already turned | my elite team into Zombies!
The dark elite has not finished her training yet. | I can't send her into battle yet.
Luckily I put my best researcher on finding| a cure against this zombie virus.
I am still working on the cure boss! I need more time!
Watch out for those | zombies and don't let them scratch you!
I found a zombie hand on the ground. | It was still alive and moving around.
I was able to run some experiments on it. | But so far no luck yet.
We need to find someone whose blood is | immune against the zombie virus.
That explorer guy looks tasty!
Get lost you Zombie fool!
We need to protect our explorer at all cost! | If he can't make the cure, all will be lost!
I was able to escape that Zombie.
I was able to protect our explorer,|but a Zombie scratched me.
Nooooooo!!! Our leader is going to turn into a Zombie!
Come Klaude! Join the Zombie side!
I am starting to feel so much power |  rushing through my blood!
No this can't be! I am changing into a...
The leader from the elite team has |joined our Zombie team now.
Yes master! I will lead our Zombies to victory.
You can't escape your destiny!
Soon everyone here will become a Zombie!
All my tests on the Zombie hand are failing. | I still don't have a working cure!
Only a miracle can save us now!
I received the message from the | Dark Elite about your Zombie situation here.
I know whose blood is immune against the Zombie virus.
My daughter got bitten by a zombie, | but she seems to be immune to the virus.
This is amazing news! | This is the miracle I was looking for!
Please take me to your daughter, | so I can take a small blood sample.
I was able to get the blood sample! I need some|more time to work on the vaccine.
Tasty brains! I want it!
You need to help me and keep|this Zombie away from me!
I did it! I was able to make 4 vaccines now!
You are brave enough to use| the vaccines on those zombies right?
Use the vaccine on the Frankenstein Zombie!!
I am so hungry! I will eat you both!
What just happened? And why are | you looking so strange at me?
Yes!!! The vaccine worked! | I am a genius!
The last thing I remember was that | some Zombie was trying to eat me.
We need to cure all the elite!
Why don't you come a little closer? | And let me bite you!
So my pirate disguise plan worked right? | I fooled those zombies big time!
Well not exactly. | But good to see you normal again.
Where are Frankenstein and the Pirate Zombie? | What did you do to them?
Dude! Why did I have 2 big horns on my head?
We did it again! But we only | have 1 more vaccine left!
Why are the elite back to normal again?
Don't worry master! | I will bite the boy into a Zombie!
Your vaccine is not powerful enough on me!
Yes Klaude, you can do it! | Fight that cure!
I was able to make 1 more vaccine! | Klaude will not be able to handle another vaccine shot!
Your vaccine shot did not work on me! | I will get you this time!
Klaude I command you to stop the boy!
You are forgetting about 1 thing Mister Pumpkin. | I am the boss around here!
Now that sounds like the Klaude I know! | Welcome back boss!
That was very smart to use a | vaccine to stop my zombie virus.
I dare you to accept my special fire type challenge!
As a special prize I will give | you the legendary Scarykin Dynamon.
You may have won this challenge! But I dare you | to meet me again for a new challenge!
I was able to make some more vaccines | and was able to cure all Zombies!
I am back baby!
I am still hungry! | Just kidding. The cure worked!
